name: Supacell
overview: When five ordinary South Londoners discover they have extraordinary powers, it's down to just one man to bring them together to save the woman he loves.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: In South London, a group of normal people suddenly develop superpowers, and the only apparent connection between them is that they are all Black; as they deal with the impact of their powers on their daily lives, one man must bring them together.

episodes.name: Michael
episodes.overview: Delivery driver Michael has big plans for the future with his girlfriend. Until something odd starts happening to him and others across South London.

episodes.name: Tazer
episodes.overview: Four Londoners reel from the discovery of their powers, while another knows exactly how to make the most of his. Michael desperately looks for answers.

episodes.name: Sabrina
episodes.overview: Sabrina and Sharleen plan a night out after a long day. The Tower Boys get into a fight that leaves Tazer swearing revenge. Michael comes up with a plan.

episodes.name: Andre
episodes.overview: Andre makes a dangerous decision after the bailiffs pay him a visit. Rodney's business slows down, and Dionne meets the mother of a missing girl.

episodes.name: Rodney
episodes.overview: With his best friend in hospital, Rodney has a change of heart. Michael resolves to telling Dionne everything — but first he has to find the others.
